00:03:50,890 --> 00:03:54,760
there were times in which
pursuing and being involved

92
00:03:54,760 --> 00:03:57,160
in work and pursuing
degrees and finding

93
00:03:57,160 --> 00:04:00,820
meaning in my vocation
