on a regular basis

100
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:16,990
oftentimes contradict
with the pressures

101
00:04:16,990 --> 00:04:19,060
and the requirements
of not just daily life

102
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:21,250
but in building a
life that allows

103
00:04:21,250 --> 00:04:23,890
us to have the kind of
resources that we need in order

