00:04:28,390 --> 00:04:31,360
and opportunity to get regular
exercise and great nutrition,

106
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,590
et cetera, et cetera.

107
00:04:32,590 --> 00:04:34,690
So, again, while this
isn't necessarily

108
00:04:34,690 --> 00:04:36,850
a complaint with any
of the research out

109
00:04:36,850 --> 00:04:39,910
of the fields of
psychology on happiness,

110
00:04:39,910 --> 00:04:42,460
it is important
that we acknowledge

111
00:04:42,460 --> 00:04:45,202
these contradictions that
exist in the discussion

112
00:04:45,202 --> 00:04:45,910
around happiness.

113
00:04:45,910 --> 00:04:48,040
In particular, the
popular discussions

114
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,790
around the science of happiness.

115
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:52,420
So today, what we are
going to arrive at,

116
00:04:52,420 --> 00:04:54,040
what you will
finish this episode,

117
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:57,520
with is a set of tools and a
framework for understanding

118
00:04:57,520 --> 00:05:00,070
