your journey or the landscape

124
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:16,240
around happiness in your
pursuit of happiness.

125
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:18,550
And what I won't
tell you is that you

126
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:20,470
need to abandon
all goals in terms

127
00:05:20,470 --> 00:05:23,890
