we have nutrition,

982
00:41:35,190 --> 00:41:36,810
we have social interactions.

983
00:41:36,810 --> 00:41:38,730
We have purposeful
work, whether or not

984
00:41:38,730 --> 00:41:40,650
it's paid work or non-paid work.

985
00:41:40,650 --> 00:41:43,980
And, of course, there
are things like exercise

986
00:41:43,980 --> 00:41:47,070
and maybe relationships to
pets and things of that sort.

987
00:41:47,070 --> 00:41:49,060
And there are a
few others as well.

988
00:41:49,060 --> 00:41:51,660
All of those are known to
increase your overall state

989
00:41:51,660 --> 00:41:54,120
of well-being, that
puts you in a position

990
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:56,910
to access more meaning
