991
00:41:56,910 --> 00:41:58,980
But for most
people, I think it's

992
00:41:58,980 --> 00:42:01,200
fair to say that
earning a living.

993
00:42:01,200 --> 00:42:05,490
And earning a living by working
is the typical way in which

994
00:42:05,490 --> 00:42:07,120
we spend most of our time.

995
00:42:07,120 --> 00:42:09,480
So I think we need to
put a special bracket

996
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:10,560
around those activities.

997
00:42:10,560 --> 00:42:12,602
And it's something we will
return to a little bit

998
00:42:12,602 --> 00:42:15,450
later in terms of trying to
understand how periods of life

999
00:42:15,450 --> 00:42:19,200
in which there are big
