1000
00:42:19,200 --> 00:42:21,450
or extensive family
demands on us

1001
00:42:21,450 --> 00:42:24,030
are indeed compatible
with states of happiness

1002
00:42:24,030 --> 00:42:27,090
or frequent states of happiness
and how better to access those.

1003
00:42:27,090 --> 00:42:30,270
Rather than simply say
money isn't important

1004
00:42:30,270 --> 00:42:32,952
or the amount of time at
work really isn't important.

1005
00:42:32,952 --> 00:42:35,160
That's not what people are
going to pay attention to.

1006
00:42:35,160 --> 00:42:37,770
In fact, I don't know how
I will feel on my deathbed.

1007
00:42:37,770 --> 00:42:39,180
How could I?

1008
00:42:39,180 --> 00:42:41,730
Human beings are pretty
good about understanding

1009
00:42:41,730 --> 00:42:43,050
how they feel in the present.

1010
00:42:43,050 --> 00:42:46,320
If not describing it, they
are pretty good at feeling it

1011
00:42:46,320 --> 00:42:49,200
if they have any sense
of internal state.

1012
00:42:49,200 --> 00:42:50,280
That is interception.

1013
00:42:50,280 --> 00:42:53,430
And you could have some idea
of how you feel in a moment.

1014
00:42:53,430 --> 00:42:57,180
We're pretty good about
describing our past feelings,

1015
00:42:57,180 --> 00:43:00,270
at least in broad
contour, but we are not

1016
00:43:00,270 --> 00:43:02,890
very good at projecting how
we will feel in the future.

1017
00:43:02,890 --> 00:43:04,307
And in fact, that's
a theme that's

1018
00:43:04,307 --> 00:43:06,540
going to come up
again and again today.

1019
00:43:06,540 --> 00:43:11,580
Nonetheless, what we do know on
the basis of really solid data

1020
00:43:11,580 --> 00:43:14,700
are that certain aspects
of our well-being

1021
00:43:14,700 --> 00:43:17,040
tend to change
across our lifespan.

1022
00:43:17,040 --> 00:43:20,130
Now lifespan is
something that we

1023
00:43:20,130 --> 00:43:22,830
need to consider from
also a bit of nuance

1024
00:43:22,830 --> 00:43:25,870
because humans are indeed
living longer and longer.

1025
00:43:25,870 --> 00:43:27,840
And if we look at
the data on happiness

1026
00:43:27,840 --> 00:43:32,430
across the lifespan dated maybe
30 or 40 years back or even

1027
00:43:32,430 --> 00:43:35,790
20 years ago, it is
consistently described

1028
00:43:35,790 --> 00:43:38,640
in that literature as a
so-called u-shaped function.

1029
00:43:38,640 --> 00:43:45,090
Where people in their 20s
report being very, very happy,

1030
00:43:45,090 --> 00:43:49,210
but as time goes on and they
acquire more responsibility.

1031
00:43:49,210 --> 00:43:51,150
So typically, getting
married and having

1032
00:43:51,150 --> 00:43:55,920
children in their mid to late
20s and 30s and into their 40s.

1033
00:43:55,920 --> 00:43:58,020
Having more work
demands, et cetera,

1034
00:43:58,020 --> 00:44:00,370
happiness tends to be
rated lower and lower,

1035
00:44:00,370 --> 00:44:01,830
at least in those
previous studies.

1036
00:44:01,830 --> 00:44:05,790
And then happiness tended
to increase as people

1037
00:44:05,790 --> 00:44:07,500
approach their 50s and 60s.

1038
00:44:07,500 --> 00:44:09,653
And they tended to retire,
and their work demands

1039
00:44:09,653 --> 00:44:11,070
were shed from
them, and they were

1040
00:44:11,070 --> 00:44:13,800
able to enjoy the small things
of life despite the fact

1041
00:44:13,800 --> 00:44:17,280
that, in general, I
would say almost always

1042
00:44:17,280 --> 00:44:20,160
people's health is not as
vigorous when they're 70

1043
00:44:20,160 --> 00:44:21,750
as it is when they're 20.

1044
00:44:21,750 --> 00:44:23,700
There are exceptions
to that, of course.

1045
00:44:23,700 --> 00:44:26,650
Of course, you can adjust the
rate of cognitive and physical

1046
00:44:26,650 --> 00:44:27,150
decline.

1047
00:44:27,150 --> 00:44:28,850
But in general,
people in their 20s

1048
00:44:28,850 --> 00:44:30,600
feel more physically
and mentally vigorous

1049
00:44:30,600 --> 00:44:33,390
than they do in their
60s and 70s, in general.

1050
00:44:33,390 --> 00:44:36,780
That u-shaped function
that I just described still

1051
00:44:36,780 --> 00:44:38,910
holds true today,
but of course, there

1052
00:44:38,910 --> 00:44:43,740
