our peers terribly much.

1194
00:50:50,500 --> 00:50:52,257
We might do that
a little bit more

1195
00:50:52,257 --> 00:50:54,590
when we're in elementary
school, high school, et cetera.

1196
00:50:54,590 --> 00:50:56,950
We're sort of age match,
maybe even college as well.

1197
00:50:56,950 --> 00:51:00,310
But an evaluation of ourselves
to our age-match peers

1198
00:51:00,310 --> 00:51:04,030
is not typically something
that we do on a daily basis.

1199
00:51:04,030 --> 00:51:06,910
Whereas on our birthday,
we get a snapshot

1200
00:51:06,910 --> 00:51:10,510
