01:02:21,030 --> 01:02:22,890
that explored
similar phenomenon.

1458
01:02:22,890 --> 01:02:25,050
So major trauma, for instance.

1459
01:02:25,050 --> 01:02:28,050
Not necessarily becoming
paraplegic but traumas

1460
01:02:28,050 --> 01:02:30,630
of a different sort,
emotional traumas.

1461
01:02:30,630 --> 01:02:33,060
When you look at the whole
