1510
01:04:48,510 --> 01:04:49,990
It's highly individual.

1511
01:04:49,990 --> 01:04:53,400
So I think those general themes
that we've heard over and over,

1512
01:04:53,400 --> 01:04:55,500
while they have merit and
they certainly stand up

1513
01:04:55,500 --> 01:04:57,870
in some of the more
powerful longitudinal

1514
01:04:57,870 --> 01:05:01,350
and short-term studies, there
