but that doesn't mean

1659
01:11:19,090 --> 01:11:21,370
that the whole notion
of synthetic happiness

1660
01:11:21,370 --> 01:11:23,230
is merely a passive
one where all we

1661
01:11:23,230 --> 01:11:26,710
