the conditions for creating

1674
01:11:59,230 --> 01:12:03,370
happiness within our mind and
in our overall state of being.

1675
01:12:03,370 --> 01:12:06,250
And she's been involved in a
number of different studies.

1676
01:12:06,250 --> 01:12:08,890
But one of the ones that I
