state of anticipation.

1698
01:13:02,860 --> 01:13:04,840
Yeah, a neural state
of anticipation

1699
01:13:04,840 --> 01:13:06,880
and not necessarily
a positive one.

1700
01:13:06,880 --> 01:13:10,120
And indeed, there are
other patterns of music

1701
01:13:10,120 --> 01:13:12,670
that involve up tones.

