01:13:34,210 --> 01:13:36,760
A lot of those patterns
of music are incorporated

1711
01:13:36,760 --> 01:13:39,760
into so-called happy
cartoons and Disney movies

1712
01:13:39,760 --> 01:13:41,230
and things of that sort.

1713
01:13:41,230 --> 01:13:46,290
In any case, Dr. Mandich and
