1714
01:13:46,290 --> 01:13:49,590
in particular, but other
features of the environment can

1715
01:13:49,590 --> 01:13:51,210
or cannot induce
states of happiness.

1716
01:13:51,210 --> 01:13:53,160
And the basic takeaway
from those studies

1717
01:13:53,160 --> 01:13:58,890
is that while having a
