1720
01:14:08,080 --> 01:14:09,750
it is not alone sufficient.

1721
01:14:09,750 --> 01:14:13,500
What is required is that
individuals not only

1722
01:14:13,500 --> 01:14:15,300
be placed into an
environment that

1723
01:14:15,300 --> 01:14:20,220
contains music or visual items
