can induce states

1725
01:14:22,620 --> 01:14:25,560
of joy or happiness or
positive anticipation,

1726
01:14:25,560 --> 01:14:29,550
but that they also are given
some sort of instruction

1727
01:14:29,550 --> 01:14:33,180
or instruction manual as
how to synthesize happiness

1728
01:14:33,180 --> 01:14:35,650
