1737
01:14:53,280 --> 01:14:56,310
Or even for people that are
very sensitive to whether.

1738
01:14:56,310 --> 01:14:59,550
There are a certain number
of individuals, about 30%

1739
01:14:59,550 --> 01:15:03,300
