1741
01:15:05,550 --> 01:15:07,890
Especially if it's been
overcast for a number of days.

1742
01:15:07,890 --> 01:15:10,770
The so-called seasonal
affective depression.

1743
01:15:10,770 --> 01:15:12,960
Those individuals,
by the way, can often

1744
01:15:12,960 --> 01:15:14,820
