make an effort to get sunlight.

1746
01:15:17,470 --> 01:15:19,970
And if they can't get sunlight,
artificial light of the sort

1747
01:15:19,970 --> 01:15:21,490
that we talked about earlier.

1748
01:15:21,490 --> 01:15:24,360
But in any case,
there are a number

1749
01:15:24,360 --> 01:15:28,380
