1759
01:15:50,890 --> 01:15:53,010
So let's better
define what that is.

1760
01:15:53,010 --> 01:15:55,530
In the case of Dr.
Mandich's work,

1761
01:15:55,530 --> 01:15:58,290
this took the form of
doing so-called happiness

1762
01:15:58,290 --> 01:16:00,000
inventories, right.

1763
01:16:00,000 --> 01:16:03,270
That can be focusing on things
that one is grateful for,

1764
01:16:03,270 --> 01:16:05,850
things that they
particularly enjoy.

1765
01:16:05,850 --> 01:16:09,390
This is somewhat of a
gratitude-type practice

1766
01:16:09,390 --> 01:16:11,220
but includes some
other features as well

1767
01:16:11,220 --> 01:16:12,930
that are more focused
on the things that

1768
01:16:12,930 --> 01:16:15,372
bring you meaning and actually
engaging in the things

1769
01:16:15,372 --> 01:16:16,330
that bring you meaning.

1770
01:16:16,330 --> 01:16:17,913
So if you're trying
to think about how

1771
01:16:17,913 --> 01:16:20,370
to improve your levels
of happiness, what

1772
01:16:20,370 --> 01:16:23,340
this research essentially
