1844
01:19:10,560 --> 01:19:13,050
Because it's simply not false.

1845
01:19:13,050 --> 01:19:15,480
It leads to the
same, as far as we

1846
01:19:15,480 --> 01:19:17,730
know, identical neurochemical
and psychological states

1847
01:19:17,730 --> 01:19:19,147
of happiness as
