1848
01:19:19,147 --> 01:19:21,090
And might even be
more persistent

1849
01:19:21,090 --> 01:19:22,440
than natural happiness.

1850
01:19:22,440 --> 01:19:24,630
It certainly, is more
under our control.

1851
01:19:24,630 --> 01:19:26,430
But the key point
