1862
01:19:52,660 --> 01:19:55,120
of Gillian Mandich and
colleagues and others

1863
01:19:55,120 --> 01:19:57,910
in the field is tremendously
important because it removes us

1864
01:19:57,910 --> 01:20:01,120
from this pressure to
just synthesize happiness

1865
01:20:01,120 --> 01:20:03,340
from within despite
our circumstances.

1866
01:20:03,340 --> 01:20:06,820
I think many of us have heard
of the incredible stories

1867
01:20:06,820 --> 01:20:10,120
of people like Viktor
