1868
01:20:10,120 --> 01:20:12,280
were stripped of
their freedom and yet

1869
01:20:12,280 --> 01:20:15,160
managed to maintain some
sense of positive anticipation

1870
01:20:15,160 --> 01:20:18,460
or at least some
sense of identity

1871
01:20:18,460 --> 01:20:21,490
that allowed them to still
access forms of happiness.

1872
01:20:21,490 --> 01:20:23,620
Those are highly unique
situations, of course.

1873
01:20:23,620 --> 01:20:26,920
And they speak to the
power of the human psyche

1874
01:20:26,920 --> 01:20:29,860
for synthesizing happiness
