1875
01:20:29,860 --> 01:20:32,620
a sense that there might
be a future and to live

1876
01:20:32,620 --> 01:20:33,670
into that future.

1877
01:20:33,670 --> 01:20:36,228
In their cases, incredibly
impressive ways.

1878
01:20:36,228 --> 01:20:38,770
But I think for most everybody,
the environment that we're in

1879
01:20:38,770 --> 01:20:40,930
has a powerful
impact on our mood.

1880
01:20:40,930 --> 01:20:43,337
And some people
more than others.

1881
01:20:43,337 --> 01:20:45,670
I know people that are perfectly
